<span id="x.v.vii"></span>

<span id="x.v.vii-p1"></span> <span class="c1"><span
id="x.v.vii-p1.1"></span>VI. <span id="fr_3601"></span>[3602](#fn_3601.md)
</span>

<span id="x.v.vii-p3"></span>He that bore up the earth was borne up on a
tree.  The Lord was subjected to ignominy with naked body—God put to
death, the King of Israel slain!

